subject: College Athletics
Swimming
lead_paragraph: Kenyon men’s swimming and diving team won its 29th consecutive N.C.A.A. Division III Swimming and Diving Championship in Oxford, Ohio. Kenyon sealed the victory by collecting three individual titles and taking the 400-yard freestyle relay.
